  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The IGC will help developing countries implement effective inclusive growth policies, in order to lift their citizens out of poverty. The programme will provide rigorous, policy-relevant research; and independent, demand-led policy advice directly to country governments on key priority areas identified in DFID&#x2019;s 2017 Economic Development Strategy: economic governance; trade and productivity; cities and infrastructure; and energy.</narrative>
